{"service_name": "Sopra Protective Monitoring", "service_id": "5953879875256320", "company_name": "Sopra Group", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Sopra Group\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Sopra Protective Monitoring\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Protective Monitoring allows an organisation to provision threat and intelligence services within their internal infrastructure. Sopra can provide consultancy on the development of this service as well as full service delivery, meeting compliancy requirements and internal security policies related to audit and alerting.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Use of cloud services to deliver protective monitoring cost effectively\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Engagement with the business to understand requirements\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Creation of an organisation threat assessment\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Definition of protective monitoring requirements based on threat assessment\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Maturity Assessment of current protective monitoring deployment against requirements\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Capacity planning assessment\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Definition and delivery of threat reports and alerts for stakeholders\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Definition and delivery of realtime, live graphical reporting\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Specification of log tampering protection\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Available in England, Scotland, Wales and Northern Ireland\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Protects critical information from unauthorised access or disclosure\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Reduces dependency on specialist security staff freeing up resource elsewhere\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Allows risks to be mitigated via implementation of appropriate security\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Continuous improvement in security measures dealing with high risk areas\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Ensures legal compliance with current directives\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Adheres to HMG policy, including mandatory requirements for Protective Monitoring\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Provides an overall view of network utilisation through flow reporting\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Ability to calculate ROI of security controls by quantifying threats\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3172 to \u00a31150 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92357/5953879875256320-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92357/5953879875256320-sfia-rate-card.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n    